data.description: Discover this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage situated on a level 1 acre lot (zoned for horses) with expansive mountain views! Home features circular driveway, private well, oversized detached 2 car garage, shed, large separate den, and master bedroom sliding door to back yard, and RV parking. This home is ready for your vision to be updated to your FOREVER HOME. Easy access to all local amenities, Lake Tahoe, and transportation from a rural, peaceful setting. Don't miss out!
